ActCooperative Credit Associations Act
SubjectExemption for Public Notices or Documents Regulations (Cooperative Credit Associations) Regulations
PrecisEXEMPTION FOR PUBLIC NOTICES OR DOCUMENTS (COOPERATIVE CREDIT ASSOCIATIONS) REGULATIONS, in order to set out prescribed circumstances under which an exemption may be granted for documents required to be made public or submitted to the Minister of Finance, Superintendent of Financial Institutions, Commissioner of the Financial Consumer Agency of Canada, or the Bank of Canada.
